vzquota - OpenVZ quota management tool
============================================

	This tool allows to manage OpenVZ quotas - both guest environments
	diskspace and inodes quotas and user/group quotas inside them.


Requirements
------------
	kernel should provide vzdquota module.


Installation
------------
	make install


Usage
-----
	See man pages and info at http://openvz.org/


